# PHSupportedMediaTypes

**Property List Key**

The types of assets a Photo Editing extension can edit.

## Photos

- **PHProjectExtensionDefinesProjectTypes**: A Boolean value indicating whether the Photos app gets a list of supported project types from an extension.
